/471254926754367/</a> <br />\n7.21 警察現場發放多枚催淚彈 22:20 Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F450544468858025%2F&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=22e9642a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/</a> <br />\n速龍小隊斥記者「係咪中立、係咪有立場」Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F631475204017598%2F&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=0fc7f38d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/</a> <br />\n【7.21 現場】警察防線前的媽媽 Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F679125395894103%2F&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=1331a79d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/</a> <br />\n【721開槍實錄】 克警濫暴，我們必定會追究到底。 林鄭，請爲每滴港人流的血負責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgodblesshk%2Fvideos%2F583308962199292%2F&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=6b1624ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/</a> <br />\n2019.07.21【中聯辦外示威者發表宣言】斥政府冷漠面對民間訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDZ6SZIliQA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDZ6SZIliQA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=f86de240\" data-aut